OL,6,FConsumer complaints about
OL,7,Fcommunications providers are up by 54%
OL,8,Fon last year, mainly because of
OL,9,Fservice quality, billing and contract
OL,10,Fissues, according to ombudsman figures.
OL,12,FThe Communications Ombudsman has
OL,13,Falready taken on 17,695 cases to June
OL,14,Fthis year, up from 11,466 cases over
OL,15,Fthe same period last year, it said.
OL,17,FCases about billing grievances have
OL,18,Falready reached 4,403 this year, up
OL,19,Ffrom 2,700 between January and June
OL,20,Flast year.
